<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA3">
<l>ivaiyaṉṟē nalla vivaiyaṉṟē tīya</l>
<l>vivaiyeṉ ṟivaiyaṟiva ṉēlu mivaiyellā</l>
<l>meṉṉā laṭaippunīk koṇṇā tiṟaiyavaṉē</l>
<l>yeṉṉāl ceyaṟpāla teṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though I know these, saying of them</l>
<l>these are not good, these are not bad, all these</l>
<l>cannot be approached or rejected by me. O lord,</l>
<l>what is it that has to be done by me?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
